							p This stage is highly decisive as you can evaluate the work of your potential architect by browsing their portfolio. As a client, you may also assess whether the architect listens to your needs and confirms that he or she understands them.
						#tabs-1-2.tab-pane.fade
							h3.title-style-1 Working on the Concept
							p The next step of our cooperation lies in developing the concept of your future home. It helps us define every single factor that makes the construction process of your home successful.
							p Our team of designers and architects has to plan every single step of the project to make sure that the final result will meet not only your requirements but also international construction and safety standards. This is when monitoring & control begin.
						#tabs-1-3.tab-pane.fade
